    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are dependable, the exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear from regular use. It has been maintained mechanically, but a buyer should expect the typical cosmetic imperfections that come with a car of this mileage. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional, honest vehicle at a fair price.",
