    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that remains in breathtaking, showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-like paint clarity and zero imperfections. The wheels are pristine, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creasing or wear, and the original protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Every electronic feature, from the immersive sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It delivers a drive that is as tight, quiet, and responsive as the day it was manufactured. This offering includes the full set of original keys, all factory manuals, and a detailed dossier of its maintenance pedigree. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
